{"tid":617931,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［學海無涯］求自學Phy Chem Bio Maths好書推介","createTime":"2018-04-05T12:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T16:56:23.000Z","uid":71878,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0ba25b7fadbb6fb01a52d3083d4860141cb3e22c","tid":617931,"uid":71878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:00:05.000Z","msg":"我覺得知識係互相緊扣，即使唔係從事相關範疇，甚至日常生活都有機會應用唔同嘅知識<br />\n<br />\n所以想睇下各位有無自學Phy Chem Bio Maths嘅好書介紹<br />\n大約高中程度，中英都可以<br />\n中學有修理科，雖然炒粉居多，但有理科底應該應付到（chem bio無讀過，完全係零）<br />\n數嘅話機率比較有興趣<br />\n<br />\n請各位不吝賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef2da5f223348940d27be140b52d096edb8a923","tid":617931,"uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:18:57.000Z","msg":"如果係興趣，先選一個topic 再用解難方向一路路搵資料一路學<br />\n<br />\n傳統教課書式的書係有系統學但悶到仆街，而且又要做練習。好以前讀書咁"},{"pid":"f57123b90befa12b7809f5db9a646f9ca2e0d868","tid":617931,"uid":130174,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:26:43.000Z","msg":"Physics for scientists and engineers : a strategic approach with modern physics / Randall D. Knight.<br />\n<br />\nChemistry / Julia Burdge.<br />\n<br />\nBiology / Kenneth A. Mason, Jonathan B. Losos, Susan R. Singer ; contributors Shelley Jansky, Tod Duncan ; based on the work of Peter H. Raven, George B. Johnson.<br />\n<br />\n三本嘢資料齊全<br />\ncover大部分高中理科<br />\n可以喺公共圖書館借<br />\n我讀嘅時侯覺得有趣<br />\n悶唔悶就見仁見智"},{"pid":"64cc7a341db63990a75a127a93d9078ce5ce4b09","tid":617931,"uid":21699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ef2da5f223348940d27be140b52d096edb8a923","tid":617931,"uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:18:57.000Z","msg":"如果係興趣，先選一個topic 再用解難方向一路路搵資料一路學<br />\n<br />\n傳統教課書式的書係有系統學但悶到仆街，而且又要做練習。好以前讀書咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:26:50.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"4e318dd02b4f4f3ae917ab5269cd1713774323bb","tid":617931,"uid":71878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc